*---------------------------------*
- Template Range Sampling Library -       http://renaud-detry.net/trsl
*---------------------------------*


* Requirements *

 Purpose              Requirement            Reference
----------------------------------------------------------------------
 Use TRSL             Boost                  http://www.boost.org
 Install TRSL         Boost+CMake            http://www.cmake.org
 Compile examples     Boost+CMake
 Compile tests        Boost+CMake
 Extract doc          Doxygen                http://www.doxygen.org


* Getting started *

 Objective                                           Command
----------------------------------------------------------------------
 Compile examples & tests                            make build
 Compile examples & tests, install TRSL headers      make install
 Extract doc                                         make doc
 Run tests (tests are silent if successful)          make test

Install prefix is /usr/local by default. If you wish to install
somewhere else, type

  make INSTALL_PREFIX=/install/prefix clean install


* Documentation *

`make doc` will generate documentation locally; see
documentation/html/index.html.

Online documentation is regularly updated, see
http://renaud-detry.net/trsl.


